what_worked: Applied single_pass_aggregation, decorrelate, pushdown, dimension_cte_isolate achieving 1.15x speedup
why_it_worked: Consolidating repeated scans into CASE aggregates reduces I/O from N scans to 1; Correlated subqueries re-execute per outer row; converting to JOIN eliminates per-row overhead; Pushing predicates closer to table scans reduces data volume in upper operators; Pre-filtering all dimension tables into CTEs avoids repeated full-table scans
